alerts.sender_name: NWS New York City - Upton (Long Island and New York City)
alerts.description:
...THE SPECIAL MARINE WARNING WILL EXPIRE AT 130 AM EDT...
The affected areas were...
Sandy Hook NJ to Fire Island Inlet NY out 20 NM...
New York Harbor...
Long Island South Shore Bays...
The thunderstorm has weakened and moved out of the warned area and
no longer poses a significant threat to boaters.
